snippet.title: NAKED CATS are way FUNNIER THAN FURRY CATS! - Funny HAIRLESS CATS compilation
snippet.description:
Cats are so cute and super funny animals, especially hairless cats! They make us laugh all the time and heal our bad mood! This funny cat compilation is the hardest TRY NOT TO LAUGH challenge! Just look how all these naked cats play, fail, get along with dogs and other animals, get scared, make funny sounds, get angry,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
